{"id": 2036, "genre": 1000, "title": "如今商家给出的哪些建议/指南/说明，你也就是随便看看？", "description": "那些真执行起来总是太繁琐而耗时费力、或者在实际情况下压根不适用的鸡肋建议，欢迎在留言区补充。", "record_count": 7999, "comment_count": 21, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201711281747562Dge80Rq7VxLdw3B.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-29T17:00:03Z", "questions": [{"id": 3344, "title": "如今商家给出的哪些建议/指南/说明，你也就是随便看看？", "content": "如今商家给出的哪些建议，你觉得参考听听就好？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 251423, "content": "一般电子产品说明书基本不看，到手到上手全靠自我摸索", "image": "img/option/option/20171128181204riGFmzDvwMZ6hVxH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251426, "content": "护肤品套装给出的繁杂步骤，一般不会参考，也不会买全套", "image": "img/option/option/20171128181629DIfw6UZpoqWGh5Ov.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251427, "content": "洗衣建议…咦标签在哪儿呢…一股脑都扔进洗衣机算了！", "image": "img/option/option/20171128181734o6RxLPzAmgOJW3h4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251428, "content": "就算过了赏味期/保质期，闻了闻好像没事也就吃了", "image": "img/option/option/20171128182050ljfVv1SGyLI7C6H0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251429, "content": "牙刷、滤芯类产品到底多久一换，不看官方建议，更倾向于搜果壳和知乎", "image": "img/option/option/201711281822405SvhVdGszLWeckQ0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251430, "content": "餐厨小家电说明书建议的食谱不太看，最终还是会看下厨房一类的菜谱", "image": "img/option/option/201711281826156KPn32ULJ84fOb7h.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251432, "content": "衣服穿搭推荐不会照单全收，通常只会买看中的单品", "image": "img/option/option/20171128182844bZhSAjkXUN7vMRWq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 251434, "content": "旅行社的路线建议基本不听，自己找攻略和资料来得更放心", "image": "img/option/option/20171128183110a1pDIgYEKRtbW5BX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}